{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.560", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der gesch\u00e4ftsf\u00fchrende Finanzminister h\u00e4lt es f\u00fcr denkbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die EU kurzfristig auf einen Fahrplan zur Vergemeinschaftung der Einlagensicherungssysteme einigt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.800", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Voraussetzung sei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.760", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Risiken in den Bankbilanzen auf ein erforderliches Minimum begrenzt w\u00fcrden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.920", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Finanzminister stellt sich hier einen l\u00e4ngeren Fahrplan vor wie damals bei der Euro-Einf\u00fchrung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.360", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben schon bei der Einf\u00fchrung der Gemeinschaftsw\u00e4hrung erleben d\u00fcrfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.600", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was von solchen geschlossenen Vertr\u00e4gen zu halten ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich nichts."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.520", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von den Maastricht-Kriterien zur Schuldenobergrenze ist nichts \u00fcbrig geblieben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.560", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vom Verbot der gegenseitigen Staatshaftung ist nichts \u00fcbrig geblieben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.600", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vom Verbot der Staatsfinanzierung durch die Europ\u00e4ische Zentralbank ist nichts \u00fcbrig geblieben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Liste ist noch l\u00e4nger; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.560", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich erspare Ihnen hier die Einzelheiten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt wird gefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.560", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Banken ihre Risiken reduzieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.040", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Risikoreduzierung bedeutet nichts anderes als den Verkauf von Forderungen mit Verlust. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.160", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hierzu brauchen Banken frisches Eigenkapital. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist aber von der EU nicht gewollt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.360", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir nehmen den Banken also quasi die Luft zum Atmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.200", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir wollen bei Bankenpleiten die betroffenen Sparer aus EU-T\u00f6pfen entsch\u00e4digen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.800", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit deutschem Geld."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der von der EU-Kommission angestrebte Transfermechanismus zwischen soliden und weniger soliden nationalen Sicherungssystemen f\u00fchrt im Kern dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.880", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass jede Bank in der Euro-Zone f\u00fcr die Risiken anderer Banken mithaften muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.120", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies f\u00fchrt dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass deutsche Sparer beispielsweise f\u00fcr die Risiken von s\u00fcdeurop\u00e4ischen Banken mithaften m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber genau diese Banken sind teilweise marode und im Kern unsolide. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Banken in S\u00fcdeuropa haben in viel zu gro\u00dfem Umfang faule Kredite in den Bilanzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.040", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen wir mit dem Geld deutscher Sparer russisches Roulette mit sechs Kugeln in der Trommel spielen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.440", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die aktuell vermeintlich gute Konjunktur fu\u00dft ganz im Wesentlichen auf der Niedrigzinspolitik der EZB; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.800", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man mag es auch Enteignung nennen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.040", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was aber passiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die Zinsen wieder steigen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann steigen die Konjunkturrisiken und damit auch die Kreditrisiken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.120", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und wir Deutschen sollen dann \u00fcber eine Bankenunion den Deckel zahlen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.680", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was soll dieser Unsinn? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im kleinen Zypern wurden die Sparer bereits rasiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.280", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Griechenland-Abenteuer haben wir mit einem blauen Auge \u00fcberstanden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.800", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.360", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Milliarden werden wir wahrscheinlich nie wiedersehen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber sie stehen noch in den B\u00fcchern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Glauben Sie tats\u00e4chlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.200", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es besser wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man jetzt Zusatznetze f\u00fcr Finanzjongleure spannt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.600", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in die sie sich jederzeit fallen lassen k\u00f6nnen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.960", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unglaublich!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen wir einmal nach Italien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.320", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das \u201eHandelsblatt\u201c hat geschrieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass 360\u00a0Milliarden Euro an faulen Krediten in den Bilanzen italienischer Banken stehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.720", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gr\u00fcnde liegen in der schleppenden italienischen Konjunktur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.480", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem schwachen Immobilienmarkt in Italien und ganz wesentlich in der schlampigen Kreditvergabepraxis. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der italienische Staat w\u00fcrde die Banken gerne st\u00fctzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wiederum m\u00f6chte die EU nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die EU m\u00f6chte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Banken die faulen Kredite abbauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.800", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also die Forderungen mit Verlust verkaufen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.920", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um diese Verluste schultern zu k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "br\u00e4uchten die Banken frisches Eigenkapital, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.680", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das der Staat im Zweifel auch gerne zuschie\u00dfen m\u00f6chte; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.200", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber die EU verbietet es wieder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.280", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Merken Sie etwas? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.520", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber diese Vergemeinschaftung der Sicherungssysteme haftet letzten Endes doch nur der deutsche Sparer."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.080", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So funktioniert das mit uns nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.160", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.800", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist absolut richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ein gemeinsamer Verbleib in der Euro-Zone nur funktionieren kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.160", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die Standards in der Euro-Zone weiter vereinheitlicht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.280", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit m\u00fcsste aber die EU den einzelnen Staaten immer mehr Vorschriften machen und die souver\u00e4nen Rechte entziehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.240", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie das? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.560", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Schulz w\u00fcrde Ihnen Beifall klatschen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.640", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute ist er nicht hier; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.120", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deswegen kann er es nicht\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "293.760", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir machen es aber nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "293.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.880", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Sinne eines guten Europas, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eines Europas der Vielfalt und der Kulturen halten wir den Euro und das hiesige Ansinnen f\u00fcr kontraproduktiv."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "303.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.880", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sollten uns besser mit einem geordneten Ausstiegsszenario besch\u00e4ftigen als mit dieser Utopie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.080", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir lehnen ein europ\u00e4isches Einlagensicherungssystem entschieden ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.400", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.280", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "317.120", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chster, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "317.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.920", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.000", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Kollege Dr.\u00a0Florian Toncar f\u00fcr die Freien Demokraten."
   ]
  }
 ]
}